TEXT.S: = Silangkong = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Yurisyang ka alang Silangkong. 290 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 834 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 30% niqan 249 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 70% niqan 585 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis15%, Bunun2%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq1%, ni rahuq na o1%.
